  "1769100": {
    "name": "Cosmic: A Journey Among Shadows",
    "steam_appid": 1769100,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/30b30d841183c7bf3d70fc5f4b3a5127.poster.avif?t=1747222996\" width=600 height=176 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/30b30d841183c7bf3d70fc5f4b3a5127.webm?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/30b30d841183c7bf3d70fc5f4b3a5127.mp4?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>小家伙星行仔意外掉进了到处都是怪物和诡异存在的陌生世界，还把自己的影子弄丢了。他只有找到影子，才能离开这个地方，只是得先搞清楚到底发生了什么？这儿是什么地方？接下来该往哪儿走？这个奇怪又危险的世界为什么一个影子都看不到？不过有一个影子突然冒了出来，愿意一路保护他，陪他找到自己的伙伴，顺利回家。<br><br>深入探索凶险的暗影之地，揭示这个世界的秘密。渡过重重险关，，邂逅住在这里的生灵，结交战友，学习新技能，生存下去。发现光明的力量，打败黑暗世界的各路魔怪，找到朋友消失的真相。<br><br>这款2.5D银河恶魔城游戏借鉴了同类型的巅峰之作，随处可见战斗难题和移动难题，让你获得流畅的平台游戏体验。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/052f594fd98fb950c08099cb915e46ca.poster.avif?t=1747222996\" width=600 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/052f594fd98fb950c08099cb915e46ca.webm?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/052f594fd98fb950c08099cb915e46ca.mp4?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▸探索世界：</strong> 凶险重重的暗影之地分为四个界域——神秘的灵河、环境恶劣的蟹沙漠、高高在上的水母王国、还有危机四伏的冷酷丛林。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/95d50d56d0d0f532ab3031fe2852bdcd.poster.avif?t=1747222996\" width=600 height=528 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/95d50d56d0d0f532ab3031fe2852bdcd.webm?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/95d50d56d0d0f532ab3031fe2852bdcd.mp4?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▸战斗灵活：</strong> 攻击、闪躲、跳跃，将攻击招式串成破坏力满满的组合连击。你的战友是一个猛兽的影子，借助它的力量打败敌人。不过，记住一点——有光的地方才能看见影子……<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/8e25e4cbdf9e5e746b41e3e056996a8f.poster.avif?t=1747222996\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/8e25e4cbdf9e5e746b41e3e056996a8f.webm?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/8e25e4cbdf9e5e746b41e3e056996a8f.mp4?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▸角色成长：</strong> 幽螟是暗影之地魔法能量的来源，捕捉这种虫子可以解锁有用的新技能，完全释放星行仔的潜能。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/c4396de6d72f032750d5e2012f5fcaa2.poster.avif?t=1747222996\" width=600 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/c4396de6d72f032750d5e2012f5fcaa2.webm?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/c4396de6d72f032750d5e2012f5fcaa2.mp4?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▸头目战刺激：</strong> 会有各种各样武力值爆棚的怪物拦住你的去路。不同的头目需要不同的策略应对，避开致命攻击，巧妙运用你的独特技能取得胜利！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/739fed99000121582ac0d27a38e69713.poster.avif?t=1747222996\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/739fed99000121582ac0d27a38e69713.webm?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/739fed99000121582ac0d27a38e69713.mp4?t=1747222996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>▸各种秘密等你揭晓：/b] 这个世界有很多隐蔽的地方和神秘的生灵。有一些生灵是真心想帮助你，其他的那些则希望你会有所回报。深入发掘暗影之地的历史，更好地了解自己来到这里的原因。有些东西知道了之后，说不定后面就会有什么好处。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>当心……你永远都不知道暗影后面下一秒会出现什么！</strong></h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1769100/extras/d38c5d5875e589ac26f4f6ff2176b85e.webp?t=1747222996\" width=616 height=16 /></span><br></strong>",
